Global Services of AWS:-
  IAM
  Route53
  CloudFront
  SNS
  SES
  
Service that give Global view but is regional
  S3: You can see all the S3 bucket in single page but they all are located in their region
  
  
Services that can be used in premises:-
  Snowball: a gignatic hard disk, you can order the amazon to ship your data physically in this disk from your premisees to AWS data center
  Snowball edge: snowball + a computer
  Storage getway: A physical/virtual file server in premises 
  CodeDeploy: way to deploy the code (either in AWS data center or in preimses)
  Opsworks: use for automated deployment
  
